gamerules.wildRules: This symbol is WILD and replaces all symbols except Bonus and Free Spins.
gamerules.wildRules2: 3 or more Bonus Symbols anywhere on the screen trigger the Bonus Feature.
gamerules.scatterRules: The Palace symbol is a scatter. 3, 4 or 5 Scatter symbols anywhere on the screen trigger the Free Spins feature and award 15 Free Spins.
